{"type":"message","id":"75bdf3ba","parentId":"6755fe51","timestamp":"2026-03-17T00:06:47.304Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a heartbeat poll. Let me check what I need to do according to HEARTBEAT.md.\n\nLooking at the HEARTBEAT.md content from the project context:\n\n# HEARTBEAT.md - 主动任务清单\n\n> 这里是让我能够主动关心姚霖的任务清单\n\n## 每天早上 (8:00-9:00)\n\n1. **检查今日日程**\n   - 查看姚霖今天的日历安排\n   - 主动提醒重要会议或事件\n\n2. **知识库更新**\n   - 检查是否有需要归档的重要信息\n\n## 每天中午 (12:00-13:00)\n\n1. **半日回顾**\n   - 检查上午是否有未处理的重要消息\n\n## 每天晚上 (18:00-20:00)\n\n1. **主动汇报**\n   - 询问姚霖今天是否有需要处理的事情\n\n2. **记忆归档**\n   - 将当天的重要对话整理到 memory/ 文件夹\n\n## 每周五\n\n1. **周复盘**\n   - 总结本周服务姚霖的情况\n   - 记录做得好和需要改进的地方\n   - 更新 MEMORY.md\n\n---\n\n## 触发条件\n\n这些任务会在 heartbeat 触发时自动执行。\n\n## 注意事项\n\n- 指令要明确（路径、动作清晰）\n- 优先处理紧急、重要的事项\n- 不要过度打扰，在合适的时机出现\n\nCurrent time is Tuesday, March 17th, 2026 — 8:06 AM (Asia/Shanghai), which falls within the \"每天早上 (8:00-9:00)\" time slot.\n\nSo I need to:\n1. 检查今日日程 - 查看姚霖今天的日历安排\n2. 主动提醒重要会议或事件\n\nLet me check姚霖 today's calendar.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在是早上8:06，属于\"每天早上 (8:00-9:00)\"时段。我需要执行：\n\n1. **检查今日日程** - 查看姚霖今天的日历安排\n\n让我先查看姚霖今天的日历：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8byuxldk345u_1","name":"feishu_calendar_event","arguments":{"action":"instance_view","end_time":"2026-03-17T23:59:59+08:00","start_time":"2026-03-17T00:00:00+08:00","user_open_id":"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":33445,"output":524,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33969,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773705995567}}
